This paper deals with a communication system involving interference channels and relays, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the optimization of the system, which involves control and systems theory (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multiple antennas, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and communication engineering (cs.CE).
